abstract.para:
The &yast; &productcreator; is a unified graphical front-end for &kiwi;
and &addoncreator;. It was developed to provide image creation
functionality in one place. All tools integrated in the &yast;
&productcreator; are also available as separate &yast; modules or
applications.

step.para:
Choose Create New to start the &yast; &addoncreator;
for setting up a new software source. Once finished, start the &yast;
Installation Sources module and add the source you
just created. Restart the &productcreator; to make the source available
for selection.
